  "detailed_description": "Become a waiter at Wacky Burgers.<br>You'll be greeted by \"look-alike\" animals, robbers, zombies... and all sorts of other customers.<br>This is an innovative point-and-click game with hand-drawn art.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Serve food quickly</h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2872800/extras/bce25c69adfcb83c2670b3ab80e55663.poster.avif?t=1753851167\" width=560 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2872800/extras/bce25c69adfcb83c2670b3ab80e55663.webm?t=1753851167\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2872800/extras/bce25c69adfcb83c2670b3ab80e55663.mp4?t=1753851167\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>.<br>Quickly select the food ordered before the restaurant's reputation drops to zero.<br>When you're not sure what to order, your instincts will come into play!<br>You may have to deal with garbage and insects... and you may have to work on your aiming skills.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Extreme service! </h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2872800/extras/d6554444c0a3ec957200b42d752dab42.poster.avif?t=1753851167\" width=560 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2872800/extras/d6554444c0a3ec957200b42d752dab42.webm?t=1753851167\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2872800/extras/d6554444c0a3ec957200b42d752dab42.mp4?t=1753851167\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>.<br>For a variety of customers, Wacky Burgers offers an action-packed service.<br>Greetings, shotguns, strong winds, drops... we are flexible and respond with the best service.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Make lots of money</h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2872800/extras/54de59fd6dd0e0e1aecb0054cd79a609.poster.avif?t=1753851167\" width=560 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2872800/extras/54de59fd6dd0e0e1aecb0054cd79a609.webm?t=1753851167\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2872800/extras/54de59fd6dd0e0e1aecb0054cd79a609.mp4?t=1753851167\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>.<br>As you reach your sales goals, your clientele and services will increase.<br>Expand your business with the money you earn! You can earn even more money.",
  "about_the_game": "Become a waiter at Wacky Burgers.<br>You'll be greeted by \"look-alike\" animals, robbers, zombies... and all sorts of other customers.<br>This is an innovative point-and-click game with hand-drawn art.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Serve food quickly</h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2872800/extras/bce25c69adfcb83c2670b3ab80e55663.poster.avif?t=1753851167\" width=560 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2872800/extras/bce25c69adfcb83c2670b3ab80e55663.webm?t=1753851167\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2872800/extras/bce25c69adfcb83c2670b3ab80e55663.mp4?t=1753851167\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>.<br>Quickly select the food ordered before the restaurant's reputation drops to zero.<br>When you're not sure what to order, your instincts will come into play!<br>You may have to deal with garbage and insects... and you may have to work on your aiming skills.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Extreme service! </h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2872800/extras/d6554444c0a3ec957200b42d752dab42.poster.avif?t=1753851167\" width=560 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2872800/extras/d6554444c0a3ec957200b42d752dab42.webm?t=1753851167\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2872800/extras/d6554444c0a3ec957200b42d752dab42.mp4?t=1753851167\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>.<br>For a variety of customers, Wacky Burgers offers an action-packed service.<br>Greetings, shotguns, strong winds, drops... we are flexible and respond with the best service.<h2 class=\"